snippet.textDisplay:
Lyrics

Kivein tenu main vikhawan
Dilon russ gayiyaan chavaan
Teri yaadan ich bikhraan main duniya sajaawan
Sun ve main kithe jaawan
Hun chup gayiyaan raawan
Main te dassiyan si khaaba ich takeya si
Ve hun din vi ni chareya ki dil ich tu mere man ich tu jadon vi ni hondi pass te tadapti ae rooh te
Rainvi tu karib soni hali na tu ja tu hi hai mera naseeb kadi na jave door
Assi laadete jinne vi tu mangdi ae taare
Meri jaan kadi vi na dare mere pyaare
Dil ich tu meri hazrat tu assi tere utte marde ne sundi nai kyun
Hun te roz tenu chaande jaande
Tere husn te marde assi roz ki kariye sajna bol
Tere hi jhol utte nachde saare
Tere pyaar ch kariye ki hun bol sajna kya aavaan kol

Kinna puch ve saans kithe rakhde ne
Gallan taalde te naal kivein hass de ne
Chad diti main ummeedaan saari duniya to
Aavein loka diyan gallan ech phasde ne
Ni main ni boldiyaan jhut mere tera hi suroor tere utte likha gaane sone jachde ne
Dilaan di yaari sadde vi dilaan da naiyo e kasoor naal rehna si zaroor sadde te iraade
Mera koi hor nai ae dass deta duniya nu
Jadon vi aave apne naal lave khushiyan nu
Jadon vi door jaave jaan saddi kat jaave
Sajna ve tere kol wasna hi chaave
Muskura ke lae liti hai saddi zimmevari
Ni main ni kitti gaddi vi tere to badgumani
Tu mera yaar si dil aasman par si yan
Do dilaan da pyaar si oh pyaar na si kaagzi par
Meri khwahish tu
Meri hazrat tu assi tere utte marde ne mande nai kyun
Hun te roz tenu chaande jaande
Tere husn te marde assi roz ki kariye sajna bol
Tere hi jhol utte nachde saare
Tere pyaar ch kariye ki hun bol sajna kya aavaan kol

Tere te main vaari jaawaan
Tere dhun gaawaan main
Tere bin jee lagda nai ae
Bass tenu chaavaan main hun raawaan mod
Hun te roz tenu chaande jaande
Tere husn te marde assi roz ki kariye sajna bol
Tere hi jhol utte nachde saare
Tere pyaar ch kariye ki hun bol sajna kya aavaan kol
